Making a folder for project
creat project react-js directory run commad in terminal "npm install -D tailwindcss"
creat css directy in project run command in terminal "npx tailwindcss init"
Type this command in terminal and run it to add some packages of react-js "npm install --legacy-peer-deps @react-three/fiber @react-three/drei maath react-tilt react-vertical-timeline-component @emailjs/browser framer-motion react-router-dom"
Update all codes in GitHub by GitHub changes view option Allways write msg in command section to save changes in github
Apter the writing basic code for web-site run terminal
then run command "npm run dev"